snippet.title: Cat Cafe Manager - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1354830/Cat_Cafe_Manager/
Discord: https://discord.gg/sAXW2mx
Sign up for the newsletter (get some in-game cats!): http://eepurl.com/g-tXBr

Become the manager of your granny's old cat cafe. Hire staff, decorate your cafe and adopt stray cats. Each cat is unique: with its own look, stats, and personality. It's your job to pick out the right combination of cats, foods and decorations to please and relax your guests.

We at Roost Games are incredibly excited to share this new business management sim!
Come hang on the Discord to talk cats!

Song: 'Dogsitting', from the album 'More Beats' by Louie Zong.
https://louiezong.bandcamp.com/track/...
(We adore Louie's work, give it a listen!)
